Trinity::

"Oh you want me to be look out? OK."

She went outside and walked around the ship.  She walked on all 
fours, her head held high and her little chest puffed out.  She 
walked around the ship in a slightly off beat military march.  She 
growled every once in a while and kept a looks out.

She saw some movement in the bushes. "HALT, WHO GO THERE?"  She stood 
her ground and looked a the bushes as they rattles.  She fired her 
tiny optic lazars into the plants. A squirrel ran out of the bush and 
up along the side of the tree, then jumped into the high branches.  
She lost sight of the squirrel.  She smiled, puffed up her chest and 
continued to march around.
